
fasauth.py:
===========

  Is the Askbot plugin to facilitate Fedora Accounts System(FAS) user
authentication. It uses python-fedora package to send the authentication
requests.

    python-fedora -> https://fedorahosted.org/python-fedora

fasauth.py exports a single API which is used by the Askbot server to perform
authentication. It returns True or False based on the authentication result.

    boolean check_password(username, password)


Install:
=========

    # python setup.py install


Bugs:
=====

